Package io.wcm.wcm.commons.contenttype

Class ContentType

java.lang.Object
io.wcm.wcm.commons.contenttype.ContentType
@ProviderType public final class ContentType extends Object
Frequently used content types/mime types. All mime types that that require encoding definition include UTF-8 as charset.
